00:20:39,599 --> 00:20:42,668
Yes. Mia.

418
00:20:42,903 --> 00:20:44,670
You liked her ?

419
00:20:44,705 --> 00:20:45,938
Pretty. Soft.

420
00:20:46,072 --> 00:20:47,807
She smelled nice.

421
00:20:49,142 --> 00:20:51,043
